Three exercise tests were performed for each subject on an electromagnetically braked cycle ergometer (Ergoline 800, Sensor Medics) with the subjects maintaining a pedaling frequency of 60 rpm. At the beginning an incremental test was performed to establish the individual subject’s maximal workload when EFL was imposed \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
\usepackage{amsmath}
\usepackage{wasysym} 
\usepackage{amsfonts} 
