\begin{document}$$\left({{W}_{\hbox{max}}}_{{\hbox{EFL}}}\right)$$\end{document} for 6 min in both protocols. At the end of exercise, EFL was removed and recovery was monitored for an additional 6 min (Fig. 1).Fig. 1
