\begin{document}$${{\dot{V}}\hbox{O}_{2}}$$\end{document} (1.7 l min−1) as the one reached in the present study during control exercise. In conditions where exercise is sustained at a moderate intensity, as in the control test, the off-transient slow component is often not discernible such that \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
\usepackage{amsmath}
